OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778054737
OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,F"Institutional misogyny" contributed
OL,8,Fto "clear warnings signs" being missed
OL,9,Fin the initial police investigation
OL,10,Ffollowing the murder of showjumper
OL,11,FKatie Simpson in Co Londonderry in
OL,12,F2020, an independent review has found.
OL,14,FA wide ranging report into the murder
OL,15,Fof showjumper Katie Simpson has
OL,16,Frevealed a series of systemic failures
OL,17,Fin policing and safeguarding in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@XO]pD@DOUpD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778054737
OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,FThe review, commissioned by Northern
OL,8,FIreland's Justice Minister Naomi Long,
OL,9,Fexposed numerous missed opportunities
OL,10,Fand failures to protect the talented
OL,11,Fshowjumper from Jonathan Creswell. He
OL,12,Ftook his own life in April 2024, after
OL,13,Fthe first day of his trial for her
OL,14,Fmurder.
OL,16,FThe report by Dr Jain Melia, former
OL,17,Fchief executive of Women's Aid
OL,18,FFederation NI, warns that the 21 year
OL,19,Fold was at risk from the moment she
OL,20,Fstepped into the unregulated yard
OL,21,Fwhere Creswell worked.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778054737
OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,FIt describes Creswell as a man who hid
OL,8,Fin plain sight, using sex abuse and
OL,9,Frape as a tactic to target women,
OL,10,Fwhile his abusive behaviour was
OL,11,Ftolerated by those around him.
OL,13,FSince the review began, more than 37
OL,14,Falleged victims of Creswell have come
OL,15,Fforward.
OL,17,FOne of those abused was Katie's sister
OL,18,FChristina, who has waived her right to
OL,19,Fanonymity, within the report.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778054737
OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,FIt is already known that Creswell had
OL,8,Fa violent past. He was jailed in 2010
OL,9,Ffor a serious assault on an ex-
OL,10,Fgirlfriend and known to the PSNI.
OL,12,FA Police Ombudsman investigation has
OL,13,Falready found the initial
OL,14,Finvestigation into Katie's death was
OL,15,F"flawed" and failed the family.
OL,17,FWhat report said about PSNI culture
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778054737
OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,FThe PSNI initially treated Katie's
OL,8,Fdeath in 2020 as suicide with the
OL,9,FOmbudsman criticising the "lack of
OL,10,Finvestigative mindset" by police.
OL,12,FHowever, this latest report from Dr
OL,13,FMeila goes further. It says the PSNI
OL,14,Finvestigation was "a profound failure,
OL,15,Fcharacterised by missed red flags,
OL,16,Fweak leadership, weak decision making
OL,17,Fand a culture of misogyny and
OL,18,Fcomplacency that marginalised Katie
OL,19,FSimpson."
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@VO]vD@SOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778054737
OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,FIt adds that failings in the case were
OL,8,F"deeply embedded in the cultural
OL,9,Fframework of the PSNI."
OL,11,FIt says that despite Creswell being in
OL,12,Ffrequent contact with police, "there
OL,13,Fwas no sustained police effort to
OL,14,Fapprehend him or develop a
OL,15,Fcomprehensive profile of his
OL,16,Fbehaviour."
OL,18,FThe report also looks at other
OL,19,Fagencies which came into contact with
OL,20,FKatie Simpson.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@WO]tD@_OUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778054737
OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,FIt reveals that at the age of 16,
OL,8,FKatie was a stowaway on the ferry to
OL,9,FScotland. She was brought back to her
OL,10,Fparents. but authorities did not refer
OL,11,Fthe matter, describing it as a missed
OL,12,Fopportunity to find out if she was
OL,13,Fcoerced or trying to escape harm.
OL,15,FKatie Simpson also attended emergency
OL,16,Fdepartments 16 times between 2003 and
OL,17,F2020 with serious injuries - including
OL,18,Fa broken back, but again authorities
OL,19,Fdid not investigate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778054737
OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,FThe report concludes that her death
OL,8,F"exposed systemic failures in policing
OL,9,Fand safeguarding practice in Northern
OL,10,FIreland" adding that she was "let down
OL,11,Fat every step."
OL,13,FIt adds that "Creswell's ability to
OL,14,Fact with impunity, was enabled by gaps
OL,15,Fin regulation/safeguarding."
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@HO]rD@^OUsD@OO]uD@NOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778054737
OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,F"Creswell posed a significant and
OL,8,Fongoing risk to women around him. The
OL,9,Fpattern of coercive and violent
OL,10,Fbehaviour that emerged after Katie's
OL,11,Fdeath had gone unrecognised and
OL,12,Funchallenged," the report details.
OL,14,FGiven these multiple failures, the
OL,15,Freport concludes that whilst Katie's
OL,16,Fdeath could not have been predicted,
OL,17,Fshe could, and should have been
OL,18,Fprotected.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
