OL,3,CPSNI 'institutional misogyny'
OL,4,Ccontributed to Katie Simpson murder
OL,5,Cprobe failings
OL,7,FWhilst revealing these multiple
OL,8,Ffailures, the report also provides a
OL,9,Fcomprehensive range of recommendations:
OL,11,FUTV has contacted the various agencies
OL,12,Fcriticised within this review,
OL,13,Foffering them the opportunity to
OL,14,Fprovide a response.
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,17,FITVX
